                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/18086344/#comments">2回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                  2012-05-02 13:44
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="18384346">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/xiaochou2046/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2541693-3.jpg" alt="Mountain Mama" class="" /></a>
